HEADWORD: Thuyin
<hw>Thu"yin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
substance extracted from trees of the genus <gen>Thuja</gen>, or
<gen>Thuya</gen>, and probably identical with quercitrin.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>thujin</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
